divs: Sighting Detailshi , just thought i would send you this photo i took whist on holliday in north wales. maybe its nothing but it spooks me. i was taking a longtime exposure of the stars moving accross the sky at haven holliday camp in pwellheli north wales and was baffled when the photo showed a disc like object in the sky. there is some camera flare from a street light at the edge of the photo but i cant see how that could account for the disc like object. please take time to look and let me know what you think.
